Codehesion makes it easy for South African companies to get their own Android and iOS smartphone apps and improve their operations. Codehesion is South Africa’s top mobile app developer and has helped many companies to build and launch world-class apps. With the rapidly changing business environment, and mobile app has become an essential addition to any business’ operating environment. Unless a business has its own app on their clients’ smartphone, they stand to lose out to their competitors. This is why many businesses are now investing in new smartphone apps, or improving on their current apps, to stay relevant. It is not only consumer-facing apps which are changing the way people do business, however. Many businesses have launched internal company apps to improve their operational efficiency and increase staff productivity. This is particularly important in the current environment where remote working has become the norm. Internal company apps also offer secure communications, company alerts, location-based task tracking, and task automation. Codehesion has many experienced mobile app developers who can help companies with their mobile app strategy and advice on which features to include. Codehesion CEO Hector Beyers said their experience also helps them guide clients on which type of app will work best for their business. Codehesion offers South African businesses a free and easy consultation process. Beyers encouraged companies who are looking for a new Android or iOS app to contact them via their website. For a risk-free consultation – Contact Codehesion here. This article was published in partnership with Codehesion.